No. 322 Squadron Crest

RNLAF F-16AM #J-063 "MiG Killer", of 322nd sqn, leaving Fairford AB on July 24th, 1999. On March 24th, 1999, this aircraft downed a Serbian MiG-29 with an AIM-120 Amraam.

Major Peter Tankink shot down a Yugoslav MiG-29 with an AIM-120A. A silhouette of a Fulcrum was painted just below the canopy rail.
